Dharmic Salad

3 ounces mixed salad greens
¼ cup broccoli sprouts
½ roasted red beet, shredded
½ large carrot, shredded
½ cucumber, sliced
½ heirloom tomato, diced
croutons
roasted sunflower kernels
parmesan cheese
ranch dressing
salt
black pepper

Makes one salad.

Add mixed greens to a large bowl. Mix in sprouts, beets, carrots, cucumber and tomatoes. Add croutons, sprinkle with sunflower kernels and cheese. Drizzle ranch all over and sprinkle with salt and pepper.

Serve immediately.
